{{#is_alert}}
A network device {{device_hostname.name}} with IP {{device_ip.name}} in namespace {{device_namespace.name}} is unreachable and can't be monitored anymore.
{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_alert_recovery}}
A network device {{device_hostname.name}} with IP {{device_ip.name}} in namespace {{device_namespace.name}} is reachable again.
{{/is_alert_recovery}}

To know more about the status of your device, you can have more information from the [NDM page for the device {{device_hostname.name}}](/devices?inspectedDevice={{device_namespace.name}}%3A{{device_ip.name}}).
